,000 crore along with the Rs. 25,000 encouragement amount for regular loans. Also Read \u2013 Chhattisgarh Farm Loan Waiver Scheme Announced in 1st Cabinet Meeting Also Read \u2013 Rajasthan Kisan Karz Mafi Yojana AnnouncedThe govt. would waive off loans taken after June 2009 (as per initial draft of Farm Loan Waiver Scheme in MP). So, this Kisan Karja Mafi Scheme will benefit around 55 lakh farmers in the state and the state govt. will have to bear an additional burden of Rs. 20,000 crore. Only those loans which had been taken for farming purposes would be included in this MP Kisan Karz Mafi Yojana. While farmers who had taken loans for purchase of tractors, agricultural machinery or any other farm equipments would not be included in this MP Kisan Karz Mafi Yojna.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}